question: Where can I find fast food restaurant on the way to Museum of Culpeper History, Culpeper, VA within 160 kilometers from 160 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.06869 38.874024)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.993306 38.472325)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.06869 38.874024)',4326)::geography, 160000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.06869 38.874024)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Sam and Joe's Pizza and Subs

[4].display_name: Museum of Culpeper History, Culpeper, VA
